title: Git & GitHub Tutorial for Scientists: It’s Not Only for Programmers
authors: Micaela Chan, Ekarin Pongpipat, & Luke Moraglia
description: A collaborative ebook that aims to provide a practical tutorial on using git and GitHub for scientists.

title: A Practical Extension of Introductory Statistics in Psychology using R
authors: Ekarin E. Pongpipat, Giuseppe G. Miranda, & Matthew J. Kmiecik
description: A collaborative ebook that aims to provide a practical extension of introductory statistics typically taught in psychology into the general linear model (GLM) using R.
